    • receiveObject

      default boolean receiveObject(Object input) throws EncryptionException, IllegalProcessException, ProcessingException
      method receiveObject

      Method called to receive an Object.

      Gibt zurück:
      boolean - true, if the object could have been handled
      Löst aus:
      EncryptionException - - thrown when the decryption process fails
      IllegalProcessException - - thrown when a process can not be performed due to unmatched requirements
      ProcessingException - - when a process can not be performed due to technical exceptions
